# Frontend

- Read `stack.config.yaml` → `frontend.framework`.
- If `none`, do not create a separate SPA (API-only / server-rendered per backend adapter).
- Otherwise follow `stacks/<frontend.framework>/CONVENTION.md` (default catalog: `react-vite`).
- Always handle loading / empty / error states.
- Access token in memory; refresh via httpOnly cookie when using the SPA auth pattern.
